How To Use Aroma Diffuser Pot: Put Around 10-15 Ml Of Aroma Diffuser Oil In The Bottle And Place Wooden Cane Reeds (4-5) In The Pot After Around 30-45 Minutes Oil Will Rise In The Wooden Reeds And Start Diffusing In The Room. For Better Aroma Effect Use It In Enclosed Space And Rotate Reeds Upside Down After Every 2-3 Days.
